## Dual Licensing Model

**Academic / Non-profit:** MIT License (fully open, free use)

**Commercial:** 
- MIT still applies (you can use it freely)
- We encourage partnership discussions
- Opportunity for joint development

**Strategic Deployments (Government, Defense):**
- Contact for custom arrangements
- Support packages available
- Exclusive features possible

